text: Lucien Masset (11 May 1914 - 17 April 2005) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:2005 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lyon
